    10: "Jupiter in the 10th house tends toward remarkable professional expansion and natural public recognition. Fortune accompanies the career, positions of authority, and the capacity to inspire by example. This placement invites one to assume a role of guide or protector in the social sphere. Abundance unfolds when outer success reflects authentic integrity and generosity.",
